# AIDAHO IDS THAS 2025

This repository contains the take-home assignment for the **AI & Data Science Certificate Hohenheim (AIDAHO)**.  
It focuses on **Automatic Identification System (AIS) data** using PostgreSQL/TimescaleDB, R, and Shiny.  

Key components:
- Querying AIS vessel data via a PostgREST API  
- Sampling and visualizing AIS points with Leaflet  
- Forecasting vessel positions and evaluating prediction accuracy  
- Building a static dashboard and deploying a Shiny app with Docker + NGINX  

Deliverables include R scripts, sampled data, visualizations, a Shiny app, and a final report.  
